original_title: Bodies of missing young woman, her baby girl found in Anguruwathota jungle
original_body_lines: The bodies of a 24-year-old woman and her 11 months old baby girl, who had gone missing a few days ago, were recovered from a jungle area at Rathmalgoda in Anguruwathota, Horana.
Police said the husband of the woman had lodged a complaint with the police claiming that his wife and baby girl had gone missing from their home when he returned.
